QUESTERA is skill-based platform for gamers and streamers where you can improve your gaming skills by playing your favorite games.
Our project was started to: 
•	Provide users with a completely new gaming experience; 
•	Enable players to challenge themselves and improve their gaming skills; 
•	Give extra pleasure from gaming and discover favorite games from a new perspective; 
•	Make it possible for players to earn on their hobby using our platform. 

Developing our own products, plunging deeply into the project and working for the long term. We use best practices and the latest technology.

We create a friendly working environment where people can do their best work and unveil their full potential.

Join us and get exceptional opportunities for learning and career growth in a comfortable and creative atmosphere.
